                 1. Tone: ${role === 'admin' ? 'Factual, Concise' : 'Meditative, Encouraging'}.
                 2. Length: **1-2 sentences**.
                 Language: **${targetLang}**.
                 Output Format (JSON ONLY): { "message": "Text...", "bgTheme": "data" }
            `;
